<H3><CENTER>Who is B.C. Ziegler and Company?</CENTER>
</H3>
B.C. Ziegler and Company is a nationwide investment banking and brokerage
firm headquartered in West Bend, Wisconsin. Throughout its history, Ziegler
has underwritten more than $20 billion of bond issues and has acquired a
reputation for safety and investor service.<BR>
<BR>
B.C. Ziegler and Company is well known for its church, healthcare and long-term
care bonds. In addition to its signature investments, Ziegler offers stocks,
mutual funds, annuities, IRAs and unit investment trusts, as well as a wide
selection of high-quality corporate and tax-exempt investment opportunities
from the secondary market.<BR>
<BR>
B.C. Ziegler and Company can help set you on the road to a more secure future.
To find out more about what Ziegler can do for you, call us toll free at
any of our <A HREF="location.htm">offices nationwide</A>.<BR>
